---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About FlowHome" description="How FlowHome reviews smart home products, handles affiliate links, and keeps automation quality controlled." canonicalURL="https://flowhome.dev/about/">
  <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-4xl rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">
    <h1>About FlowHome</h1>
    <p>FlowHome is a smart home affiliate research site focused on practical buying decisions: compatibility, setup friction, owner feedback, deal timing, and long-term utility.</p>
    <h2 id="affiliate-policy">Affiliate policy</h2>
    <p>As an Amazon Associate, FlowHome earns from qualifying purchases. Affiliate revenue keeps the site free, but products are filtered through ROI and quality gates before publication.</p>
    <h2>Automation policy</h2>
    <p>Automation assists with discovery, draft generation, quality checks, syndication, and maintenance. Content should still be useful, specific, and verifiable before publication.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
